# Iceberg 与 Flink 集成

Iceberg为Apache Flink提供了全面的集成支持，允许Flink读取和写入Iceberg表。Iceberg支持多个Flink版本（v1.15、v1.16、v1.17、v1.18）。

## 核心组件

### Flink Catalog

- [FlinkCatalog](mdc:flink/v1.17/flink/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/flink/FlinkCatalog.java): Flink目录的Iceberg实现，用于管理Iceberg表
- [FlinkCatalogFactory](mdc:flink/v1.17/flink/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/flink/FlinkCatalogFactory.java): 创建FlinkCatalog实例的工厂类

### 表工厂

- [FlinkTableFactory](mdc:flink/v1.17/flink/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/flink/FlinkTableFactory.java): 创建Flink表的工厂类
- [IcebergTableSource](mdc:flink/v1.17/flink/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/flink/source/IcebergTableSource.java): Iceberg表源的实现
- [IcebergTableSink](mdc:flink/v1.17/flink/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/flink/sink/IcebergTableSink.java): Iceberg表接收器的实现

### 数据源与接收器

- [FlinkSource](mdc:flink/v1.17/flink/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/flink/source/FlinkSource.java): 从Iceberg表读取数据的Flink数据源
- [FlinkSink](mdc:flink/v1.17/flink/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/flink/sink/FlinkSink.java): 将数据写入Iceberg表的Flink接收器

### 格式转换

- [RowDataToRowConverter](mdc:flink/v1.17/flink/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/flink/data/RowDataToRowConverter.java): 在Flink RowData和Iceberg Row之间转换
- [FlinkTypeToType](mdc:flink/v1.17/flink/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/flink/FlinkTypeToType.java): 在Flink类型和Iceberg类型之间转换

## 事务支持

- [FlinkTableOperations](mdc:flink/v1.17/flink/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/flink/FlinkTableOperations.java): Flink特定的表操作实现
- [FlinkUpsertTable](mdc:flink/v1.17/flink/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/flink/FlinkUpsertTable.java): 支持upsert操作的Flink表

## Flink SQL支持

- [FlinkDynamicTableFactory](mdc:flink/v1.17/flink/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/flink/FlinkDynamicTableFactory.java): 支持Flink SQL的动态表工厂
- [IcebergStreamWriter](mdc:flink/v1.17/flink/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/flink/sink/IcebergStreamWriter.java): 流式写入Iceberg表的写入器

## Flink CDC支持

- [RowDataTaskWriterFactory](mdc:flink/v1.17/flink/src/main/java/org/apache/iceberg/flink/sink/RowDataTaskWriterFactory.java): 处理CDC事件的任务写入器工厂

## 常见使用模式

### 批处理读写

```java
// 创建Flink表环境
TableEnvironment tEnv = TableEnvironment.create(settings);

// 注册Iceberg目录
tEnv.executeSql("CREATE CATALOG iceberg_catalog WITH (" +
    "'type'='iceberg', " +
    "'catalog-type'='hive', " +
    "'uri'='thrift://localhost:9083', " +
    "'warehouse'='hdfs://localhost:8020/warehouse/path')");

// 读取Iceberg表
tEnv.executeSql("SELECT * FROM iceberg_catalog.db.table").print();

// 写入Iceberg表
tEnv.executeSql("INSERT INTO iceberg_catalog.db.table SELECT * FROM source_table");
```

### 流式处理

```java
// 创建Flink流表环境
StreamTableEnvironment tEnv = StreamTableEnvironment.create(env, settings);

// 注册Iceberg目录
tEnv.executeSql("CREATE CATALOG iceberg_catalog WITH (" +
    "'type'='iceberg', " +
    "'catalog-type'='hive', " +
    "'uri'='thrift://localhost:9083', " +
    "'warehouse'='hdfs://localhost:8020/warehouse/path')");

// 流式写入Iceberg表
tEnv.executeSql(
    "INSERT INTO iceberg_catalog.db.table /*+ OPTIONS('write-mode'='upsert') */ " +
    "SELECT * FROM kafka_source_table");
```
